>\n分組賽中有關隊伍的對賽球差<br />\n分組賽中有關隊伍的對賽入球數字<br />\n公平競技得分 (由紅黃牌數目而定)<br />\n由國際足協籌委會進行抽籤<br />\n每組前兩名球隊將晉身十六強淘汰階段賽事。<br />\n淘汰賽階段<br />\n十六強至決賽如於法定時間賽和，則會進行加時比賽；若仍未能分出勝負，則需以十二碼決勝。<br />\n(資料更新日期︰28/11/2017 12:29) <br />\n備註: * 以上資料只供參考# 賽事於中立場舉行<br />\n注意事項：投注前敬請注意資料的更新日期及時間。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"da2eef3b26afb7c4d668e2b041bca7effe92c1ed","tid":713423,"uid":1147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:31:28.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8e46a3702a6c1790dcfff4dea902bbe3ee2693","tid":713423,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da4ed2ff8de78bccefcd30287cf3b74e736a8fa8","tid":713423,"uid":29017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"89815287346078b3b60c071365188dfa3966c29e","tid":713423,"uid":87272,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"c37abda32d9eba4da73d9216fee2c893cb0000a4","tid":713423,"uid":54876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:23:34.000Z","msg":"抽籤"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:24:20.000Z","msg":"又再一樣呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:30:17.000Z","msg":"抽籤抽一隊出線點又再一樣呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T23:39:37.000Z","msg":"由曾志偉黎抽"},{"pid":"19b1c0da1bb6f973f12f56a8ecf9253aae7b0a27","tid":713423,"uid":4431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d8e46a3702a6c1790dcfff4dea902bbe3ee2693","tid":713423,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da4ed2ff8de78bccefcd30287cf3b74e736a8fa8","tid":713423,"uid":29017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"89815287346078b3b60c071365188dfa3966c29e","tid":713423,"uid":87272,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:24:20.000Z","msg":"又再一樣呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T19:30:17.000Z","msg":"抽籤抽一隊出線點又再一樣呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T23:39:37.000Z","msg":"由曾志偉黎抽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T23:41:55.000Z","msg":"打和"},{"pid":"62c1c1257fd8ff5513cf5a5c